@startuml Create Meal Plan - Sequence Diagram

!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

title Sukurti mitybos planą - Sequence Diagram

actor "Šeimos\nnarys" as User
participant "MealPlanningPage\n<<screen>>" as Page
participant "MealPlanningController\n<<control>>" as Controller
participant "MealPlanningService" as MealService
participant "GeminiServiceBoundary\n<<boundary>>" as Gemini
participant "SpoonacularServiceBoundary\n<<boundary>>" as Spoonacular
participant "ShoppingListService" as ShoppingService
participant "InventoryEntity\n<<entity>>" as Inventory
participant "MealPlanEntity\n<<entity>>" as MealPlan
participant "SupabaseClient\n(Core.Network)" as Supabase
database "Supabase DB" as Database

== SCENARIJUS: Vartotojas sukuria naują mitybos planą ==

User -> Page: Atidaro plano generavimo formą
activate Page

Page -> Controller: OpenCreateMealPlanFormEvent()
activate Controller
Controller --> Page: CreateMealPlanFormState()
deactivate Controller

Page -> User: Rodo formą:\n- Dienos skaičius (1-7)\n- Kalorijų intervalas\n- Makroelementai\n- Alergijos\n- Dietos tipas\n- Pageidavimai
deactivate Page

== Tikslų ir apribojimų įvedimas ==

User -> Page: Suveda duomenis\nir paspaudžia "Generuoti"
activate Page

Page -> Controller: CreateMealPlanEvent(\n  days: 7,\n  caloriesRange: {min: 1800, max: 2200},\n  allergies: [...],\n  dietType: "vegetarian",\n  preferences: [...]\n)
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller: validateMealPlanInput(data)

alt Duomenys nevalidūs
    Controller --> Page: MealPlanValidationErrorState(errors)
    deactivate Controller
    Page -> User: Rodo validacijos klaidas
    deactivate Page
else Duomenys validūs
    Controller -> Supabase: from('inventory_items')\n  .select()\n  .eq('user_id', userId)\n  .is_('deleted_at', null)
    activate Supabase
    Supabase -> Database: SELECT * FROM inventory_items\nWHERE user_id = ? AND deleted_at IS NULL
    activate Database
    Database --> Supabase: Inventory items (JSON)
    deactivate Database
    Supabase --> Controller: List<Map<String, dynamic>>
    deactivate Supabase
    
    Controller -> Inventory: createSnapshot(inventoryData)
    activate Inventory
    Inventory --> Controller: InventorySnapshot
    deactivate Inventory
    
    Controller -> MealService: generateMealPlan(\n  userGoals,\n  inventorySnapshot\n)
    activate MealService
    
    == Planų generavimas (Gemini + Spoonacular) ==
    
    MealService -> Gemini: generateMealIntent(\n  caloriesRange,\n  dietType,\n  allergies,\n  preferences\n)
    activate Gemini
    
    note right of Gemini: **Gemini API:**\nGeneruoja meal-intent JSON\nsu struktūrizuotais pageidavimais
    
    Gemini -> Gemini: POST /v1/models/gemini-pro
    Gemini --> MealService: MealIntent JSON\n(structured preferences)
    deactivate Gemini
    
    MealService -> Spoonacular: searchRecipes(\n  mealIntent,\n  caloriesRange,\n  3 variants per meal\n)
    activate Spoonacular
    
    note right of Spoonacular: **Spoonacular API:**\nIeško 3 receptų variantų\nkiekvienam valgiui\n(breakfast, lunch, dinner)
    
    Spoonacular -> Spoonacular: GET /recipes/complexSearch\n+ GET /recipes/{id}/information
    Spoonacular --> MealService: List<Recipe> (3 variants per meal)
    deactivate Spoonacular
    
    MealService -> MealService: combineVariants(recipes)\n- Sujungti variantus\n- Perskaičiuoti kalorijas\n- Apskaičiuoti ingredientų panaudojimą
    
    MealService -> MealService: calculateIngredientUsage(\n  recipes,\n  inventorySnapshot\n)
    
    MealService --> Controller: GeneratedMealPlan(\n  days: 7,\n  meals: [...],\n  3 variants per meal,\n  calories: balanced ±3%,\n  ingredientUsage: {...}\n)
    deactivate MealService
    
    Controller -> MealPlan: create(generatedPlan)
    activate MealPlan
    MealPlan --> Controller: MealPlanEntity (temp)
    deactivate MealPlan
    
    Controller --> Page: MealPlanGeneratedState(\n  mealPlan: MealPlanEntity,\n  variants: [...],\n  caloriesTotal: 2000,\n  ingredientUsage: {...}\n)
    deactivate Controller
    
    Page -> User: Rodo sugeneruotą planą:\n✅ 3 variantai per valgį\n✅ Kalorijų balansas ±3%\n✅ Ingredientų integracija\n+ [Patvirtinti] + [Atšaukti]
    deactivate Page
    
    == Patvirtinimas ==
    
    alt Vartotojas patvirtina
        User -> Page: Paspaudžia "Patvirtinti"
        activate Page
        Page -> Controller: ConfirmMealPlanEvent(mealPlan)
        activate Controller
        
        Controller -> MealPlan: convertToJson()
        activate MealPlan
        MealPlan --> Controller: JSON data
        deactivate MealPlan
        
        Controller -> Supabase: from('meal_plans')\n  .insert({\n    user_id: userId,\n    plan_start_date: startDate,\n    plan_end_date: endDate,\n    meals: mealsJson,\n    locked_meals: []\n  })
        activate Supabase
        Supabase -> Database: INSERT INTO meal_plans\n(user_id, plan_start_date, plan_end_date, meals, locked_meals)
        activate Database
        Database --> Supabase: Inserted meal_plan (id)
        deactivate Database
        Supabase --> Controller: Inserted data
        deactivate Supabase
        
        Controller -> ShoppingService: generateShoppingList(\n  mealPlan,\n  inventorySnapshot\n)
        activate ShoppingService
        
        ShoppingService -> ShoppingService: calculateMissingIngredients(\n  mealPlan.ingredients,\n  inventorySnapshot\n)
        ShoppingService -> ShoppingService: groupByStore(deals)
        
        ShoppingService --> Controller: ShoppingListEntity
        deactivate ShoppingService
        
        Controller -> Supabase: from('shopping_lists')\n  .insert({\n    meal_plan_id: mealPlanId,\n    items: shoppingListJson\n  })
        activate Supabase
        Supabase -> Database: INSERT INTO shopping_lists\n(meal_plan_id, items)
        activate Database
        Database --> Supabase: Success
        deactivate Database
        Supabase --> Controller: Success
        deactivate Supabase
        
        Controller --> Page: MealPlanCreatedState(\n  message: "Planas sukurtas!"\n)
        deactivate Controller
        
        Page -> User: Rodo sėkmės pranešimą:\n✅ "Planas sukurtas!"
        deactivate Page
        
    else Vartotojas atšaukia
        User -> Page: Paspaudžia "Atšaukti"
        activate Page
        Page -> Controller: CancelMealPlanEvent()
        activate Controller
        Controller --> Page: MealPlanCancelledState()
        deactivate Controller
        Page -> User: Grįžta į pagrindinį ekraną
        deactivate Page
    endif
endif

note over User, Database
  **SVARBU:**
  - Sistema generuoja planą per Gemini + Spoonacular
  - 3 variantai per valgį
  - Kalorijų balansas ±3%
  - Automatiškai sugeneruojamas shopping list
end note

@enduml



















